## Future Vision

The long-term vision of this project is to create an intelligent AI career mentor that supports students from their first year of college until they secure a job. The assistant would continuously recommend new skills, monitor learning progress, predict placement readiness, and help students stay competitive in the rapidly changing technology industry.
